			<table width="550" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tbody><tr>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><p>Dear {!NCS_Application__c.YoungPerson__c},</p>
			<p>Since you told us you were interested in NCS, we have tried to get back in touch with you but haven't managed to speak to you. We are The Challenge, and we'll be running NCS in your area this summer. Here's a reminder of what you could be doing this summer....[OR Here's a reminder of how NCS could help you get ahead...]</p>
			<p>[INSERT TV AD]</p>
			<p>NCS is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity to meet new people, make new friends and build the skills and confidence to help you get ahead. Over 120,000 young people have already taken part - don't miss out this summer!</p>
			<p><strong>How long does it last?</strong><br>
			<strong>Part 1 - Get Active:</strong> Five days (four nights) staying away from home in the countryside doing outdoor adventure activities.<br>
			<strong>Part 2 - Get Involved:</strong> Five days (four nights) staying away from home developing skills.<br>
			<strong>Part 3 - Make Your Mark:</strong> Community activity days, staying at home at night - four during summer and four on September weekend days.</p>
			<p><strong>Is there a cost?</strong><br>
			Even though each place is valued at over £1000, thanks to government backing NCS costs you no more than a £50 admin fee. Plus, you get an extra £5 discount when you sign up online!</p>
			<p><strong>How do I apply?</strong><br>
			Go to www.NCSTheChallenge.org and use the following unique login details to apply:</p>
			<p><strong>NCS ID: {!Contact.NCS_ID__c}<br>
			Password: {!Contact.Login_PIN__c}</strong></p>
			<p>As you go through your online application, the website will tell you that some parts need to be completed by your parent or guardian, so please ask them to log in to do these.</p>
			<p><strong>Any questions?</strong><br>
			If you have any questions, get in touch by calling 020 3542 2400 or emailing contact@the-challenge.org.</p>
			<p>Places are filling up fast for this once-in-a-lifetime opportunity so act now! We'll be in touch once we've received your application.</p>
			<p>Yours sincerely,</p>
			<p>Tanya Dunne<br>
			Head of Customer Services - The Challenge</p></td>
			
